{"tid":2250074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭 ：曾有人挖角，希望我跳槽，但我仍堅持服務市民","createTime":"2020-10-20T00:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T11:33:36.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":346,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"62905e6eb1c25badda33769a365b4f1f2dbbb033","tid":2250074,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmzPXt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmzPXt7.jpg&h=2ca77854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥接受商報專訪時表示，這些年來曾有「出面人招手」希望她「跳槽」，但她仍然堅持做公務、服務市民。她強調自己從事公僕生涯40年，無懼任何打擊，「所有事都是為香港好。甚至近年工作為國家好，都是問心無愧，會繼續做」。<br />\n<br />\n至於過去曾希望每個月到立法會進行「短問短答」環節與立法會議員溝通，但林鄭月娥說如果每次出席只是製造矛盾，看不到有空間交代工作或聽取意見，就去少一些。<br />\n<br />\n對於網上各種攻擊，林鄭月娥反問「為何要花時間，去看、去聽、去不開心？不如不看、不聽。」又笑言自己已做到「百毒不侵」、「怎樣罵我都影響不到我的工作」。"},{"pid":"9420d4e3684fd3815655205f36ea38e84772f71f","tid":2250074,"uid":192726,"like":211,"dislike":1,"score":210,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"邊個第三世界國家挖角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e33c9ca4be614cbecc7be416ef5b4528a07ef4a","tid":2250074,"uid":40499,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:26:02.000Z","msg":"我唔使你服務啦 加上你無服務過市民"},{"pid":"9d09a9176add80e48492f39606f01cd9144c46c4","tid":2250074,"uid":366655,"like":86,"dislike":5,"score":81,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:26:27.000Z","msg":"做公務員仲咁高人工<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">傻嘅先會跳槽</span>"},{"pid":"a7413791ccc479771247ac90720b3a67e076aefb","tid":2250074,"uid":39710,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"希望<br />\n佢跳樓多啲"},{"pid":"05998ad17ddfaf1baf5bfae91603eff589ecc76d","tid":2250074,"uid":69707,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:28:21.000Z","msg":"閻羅王挖角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f508c547062323e8f9cbe4493c34077d311732","tid":2