ead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"共僕"},{"pid":"86129a445addc9bbb40ab6034359847bae3aafff","tid":2250074,"uid":252659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62905e6eb1c25badda33769a365b4f1f2dbbb033","tid":2250074,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmzPXt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmzPXt7.jpg&h=2ca77854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥接受商報專訪時表示，這些年來曾有「出面人招手」希望她「跳槽」，但她仍然堅持做公務、服務市民。她強調自己從事公僕生涯40年，無懼任何打擊，「所有事都是為香港好。甚至近年工作為國家好，都是問心無愧，會繼續做」。<br />\n<br />\n至於過去曾希望每個月到立法會進行「短問短答」環節與立法會議員溝通，但林鄭月娥說如果每次出席只是製造矛盾，看不到有空間交代工作或聽取意見，就去少一些。<br />\n<br />\n對於網上各種攻擊，林鄭月娥反問「為何要花時間，去看、去聽、去不開心？不如不看、不聽。」又笑言自己已做到「百毒不侵」、「怎樣罵我都影響不到我的工作」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:41:07.000Z","msg":"邊個咁睇唔開"},{"pid":"f10dc19eeb50630608ce58ebf5b7b91d5ae574c5","tid":2250074,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9420d4e3684fd3815655205f36ea38e84772f71f","tid":2250074,"uid":192726,"like":211,"dislike":1,"score":210,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"邊個第三世界國家挖角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"第三世界國家：過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf2deb8a66fb1535fa53a04c5dd22be23bbcd8c","tid":2250074,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d09a9176add80e48492f39606f01cd9144c46c4","tid":2250074,"uid":366655,"like":86,"dislike":5,"score":81,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T00:26:27.000Z","msg":"做公務員仲咁高人工<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">傻嘅先會跳槽</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"公務員？連登仔論政質素果然低下"},{"pid":"a9fe652d7626347f2c90a88049f915344a97638f","tid":2250074,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:43:18.000Z","msg"